2
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:08,410
Hello and welcome.

3
00:00:08,830 --> 00:00:12,013
This is Tomb Raider Rebooted, audio reimagined.

4
00:00:12,933 --> 00:00:14,174
My name is Jack Grillo.

5
00:00:14,194 --> 00:00:15,915
I was the lead sound designer for Tomb Raider.

6
00:00:16,476 --> 00:00:18,437
This is Alex Wilmer, music supervisor.

7
00:00:19,738 --> 00:00:21,659
This session is being recorded, so we're

8
00:00:21,959 --> 00:00:24,861
asked to ask you to please silence your cell phones.

9
00:00:25,882 --> 00:00:27,863
The talk will be broken up into a few discussions.

10
00:00:28,684 --> 00:00:31,706
I will speak about creative direction, voiceover,

11
00:00:31,746 --> 00:00:32,386
and sound effects.

12
00:00:32,827 --> 00:00:34,288
Alex will speak about music, and then we'll

13
00:00:34,328 --> 00:00:35,508
open it up for some questions.

14
00:00:37,075 --> 00:00:42,277
I'm going to start off by playing a trailer from the 2012 VGA's.

15
00:00:42,297 --> 00:00:46,558
It features our composer Jason Graves conducting a live orchestra.

16
00:01:07,915 --> 00:01:09,056
So much has happened.

17
00:01:10,016 --> 00:01:24,218
Our captain is injured.

18
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:25,539
