22
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:33,520
I've got to find them.

23
00:01:35,354 --> 00:01:37,417
We're hunted by the island's inhabitants.

24
00:01:37,477 --> 00:01:41,622
It's been so long you've walked out.

25
00:01:43,283 --> 00:01:46,547
Sam, listen. I'm going to get you out of there.

26
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:20,233
You can do it, Laura. After all, you're a Croft.

27
00:02:20,894 --> 00:02:22,175
I don't think I'm that kind of Croft.

28
00:02:22,695 --> 00:02:23,436
Sure you are.

29
00:02:23,456 --> 00:02:29,020
You just don't know it yet.

30
00:02:39,168 --> 00:02:40,549
Alright, let's do this.

31
00:03:03,412 --> 00:03:07,235
You can save everyone.

32
00:03:07,335 --> 00:03:12,579
There's no other choice. I've got to do this.

33
00:03:13,780 --> 00:03:14,841
If I don't survive...

34
